.TP 2
.B
\fI{\&'Host-IP-Address\&', [\fBAddress()\fR\&]}\fR\&:
An address list is available to the start function of a \fBtransport module\fR\&, which can return a new list for use in the subsequent CER or CEA\&. Host-IP-Address need not be specified if the transport module in question communicates an address list as described in \fBdiameter_transport(3)\fR\&
.TP 2
.B
\fI{\&'Vendor-Id\&', \fBUnsigned32()\fR\&}\fR\&:

.TP 2
