.RS
.LP
Stop a diameter service\&.
.LP
Stopping a service causes all associated transport connections to be broken\&. A DPR message with be sent as in the case of \fBremove_transport/2\fR\&\&.
.LP

.RS -4
.B
Note:
.RE
Stopping a service does not remove any associated transports: \fBremove_transport/2\fR\& must be called to remove transport configuration\&.

.RE
